====Template:VersionBox usage====
This template is translation-independent. Keep it like that! Is is used in translation specific templates like {{en/S|en/Feature}} or {{en/S|fr/Disponibilité période}}.

<pre>
<nowiki>{{</nowiki>'''Feature''' | ''Version number from'' | ''Version number to'' | '''caption=''' ''Translation-specific caption''  | '''text=''' Optional additional text <nowiki> | '''align=''' Optional box alignment}}</nowiki>
</pre>
Supported versions: 0, 0.5, 0.6, 0.7, 1.0, 1.1, 1.2 (and others can be added easily).<br/>
Use version 0 for old versions before 0.5. Use the unreleased version for nightlies.

